<div id="infobox" class="infobox"> 
 <div class="table-responsive"> 
  <table class="wiki_table"> 
   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Shard of Alexander</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img title="Shard of Alexander" src="/file/Elden-Ring/shard_of_alexander_talisman_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="shard of alexander talisman elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Weight</td> 
     <td>0.9</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <img src="/file/Elden-Ring/status_effect_2_elden_ring_wiki_guide_44px.png" alt="status effect 2 elden ring wiki guide 44px" width="20" height="20">&nbsp;Greatly boosts the attack power of&nbsp; 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Skills" href="/Skills">Skills</a>&nbsp;by 15% 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Shard of Alexander</strong>&nbsp;is a <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Talismans" href="/Talismans">Talisman</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>.&nbsp;<strong>Shard of Alexander</strong>&nbsp;greatly boosts the attack power of <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Skills" href="/Skills">Skills</a> by 15%. Players can use <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Talismans" href="/Talismans" target="">Talismans</a>&nbsp;in Elden Ring to boost a variety of <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stats" href="/Stats" target="">Stats</a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>Shard of the late Alexander, a shattered warrior jar.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Greatly boosts the attack power of skills.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Scraps of stewed flesh cling to the shard, and tatters of ornaments can be seen mingled within the slime. Relics of a red-haired champion, it would seem.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Shard of Alexander Effect in Elden Ring</h3> 
<p><strong>Shard of Alexander</strong> greatly&nbsp;boosts the attack power of&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Skills" href="/Skills">Skills</a>&nbsp;by 15% (remains 15% in PVP).</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Shard of Alexander in Elden Ring</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Shard of Alexander</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Drops from <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Iron Fist Alexander" href="/Iron+Fist+Alexander">Iron Fist Alexander</a> after completing his questline. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=5916&amp;lat=-124.554687&amp;lng=212.769601&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=5916&amp;lat=-124.554687&amp;lng=212.769601&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Video Location" href="https://youtu.be/SM11swgGzw0?t=2578">Video Location</a></li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Shard of Alexander Notes &amp; Tips</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Sell Value:&nbsp;<img title="Runes" src="/file/Elden-Ring/runes-currency-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="runes currency elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">&nbsp;1000</li> 
</ul> 
